{"tid":1449713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公投！12定17入機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:44:09.000Z","uid":120308,"like":49,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"82ab5256e8a4f95a8613fcef00d6173fb0cdcd66","tid":1449713,"uid":120308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:01:56.000Z","msg":"有post發起12號入機場和你飛，相信好多巴打都好火,想盡快出去。<br />\n<br />\n但同時有好大問題係冇12號冇時間做文宣，冇人去一定失敗。同之前已經好多人罷過工，好難聽日再罷，星期6會係一個較好聚人既時機。<br />\n<br />\n開好個頭非常重要，之後自然會多人知。同時要停止其他行動，集中火力搞機場，先後幾次機場行動都比地方遊行搶哂focus，搞到冇咩媒體播。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />12／8<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />17／8"},{"pid":"c02ddf98e4203361a0c9b9ad788cf94ea8c14286","tid":1449713,"uid":33307,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:02:27.000Z","msg":"兩日得唔得呀垃圾樓主"},{"pid":"6c559b59b7cde11aa25b92dd4de8c24a48faa6bd","tid":1449713,"uid":120308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:02:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82b3eac7b0fe841960e996f08036a55e87fcfd63","tid":1449713,"uid":176802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:12.000Z","msg":"投你老母咩投<br />\n兩日一齊搞啦"},{"pid":"7758bc00427db990fa5d819636380335325421c1","tid":1449713,"uid":120308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c02ddf98e4203361a0c9b9ad788cf94ea8c14286","tid":1449713,"uid":33307,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:02:27.000Z","msg":"兩日得唔得呀垃圾樓主"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:29.000Z","msg":"之前八五都宣左成個星期，2日都係趕啦"},{"pid":"8cc1a61534e0115acf85537c1d20a30f4bcf5552","tid":1449713,"uid":138922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:05:44.000Z","msg":"12"},{"pid":"ed3e8d94e8bab9e921d2fb8e0c035c101ca8a501","tid":1449713,"uid":296646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:05:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad9bcd5a74f